===Etymology===
{{etyl|ang}} {{term|funel|lang=ang}}, {{term|fonel|lang=ang}}, probably through {{etyl|fro}} from {{etyl|la}}
{{term|fundibulum|lang=la}}, {{term|infundibulum||funnel|lang=la}}, from {{term|infundere||to pour in|lang=la}};
{{term|in||in|lang=la}} + {{term|fundere||to pour|lang=la}}; compare Breton {{term|founil||funnel}}, Welsh {{term|ffynel||air hole, chimney|lang=cy}}. See [[fuse]].

